                    <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                        <ab>
                            <lb n="1"/><rs type="institution" subtype="practice" role="decreeing" key="andano" ref="#dreros"><w lemma="ϝανδάνω">ἔϝαδε</w></rs> τοῖ<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>ι <rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="decreer" key="thystas" ref="#dreros"><w lemma="θύστας">θύστασι</w></rs>·
                            <lb n="2"/>ὄς μέν κα δίδο̃ι <w lemma="μισθός">μισθόν</w>
                            <lb n="3"/>λαγκάνεν <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><orig><unclear>υ</unclear>ε<unclear>ι</unclear></orig><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <space quantity="1" unit="line"/>
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                        <p>Il decreto, relativo ad una remunerazione, è promosso dai <foreign>thystai</foreign> di Dreros; tali figure, non attestate altrove, possono essere identificate in funzionari religiosi equivalenti ai sacerdoti sulla base di una glossa di Esichio (<ref type="lit" target="#HschThystas">Hsch. <foreign>s.v.</foreign> θύστας</ref>· ὁ ἱερεὺς παρὰ Κρησί; cf. <bibl><ref target="#b699">Genevrois 2017</ref>, p. 178</bibl>).</p>
                <p><emph>Elementi istituzionali o altri termini rilevanti</emph>: <ref type="inst" target="#andano"><foreign>andano</foreign></ref>, <ref type="inst" target="#thystas"><foreign>thystas</foreign></ref>.</p>
                    </div>
